      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，所以起点是thanksSigningUp，它属于HealthTech_PatientRecords服务。那HIPAA验证这个节点，我理解为是HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault服务对吗？验证通过后才进入pendingApproval状态？",
